data.description: Special Financial Incentives: The seller is committed to making your dream home a reality by offering an incredible contribution of up to $20K! Use this towards new flooring, paint, closing costs, a rate buy down, or whatever suits your needs. Imagine customizing your new home exactly to your taste with this generous offer!  And there's even more good news! This home qualifies for a Bank of America grant program, offering up to $17.5K in down payment assistance. This is a golden opportunity for first-time buyers or those looking to upgrade their living experience.  This Spacious 4 Bedroom , 3.5 Bathroom home is located in Douglasville, GA near I-20. It has so many desirable features - a fenced backyard with a deck & a patio, a 2-car Garage, a brand NEW ROOF, a large master bedroom w/sitting area, formal living & dining rooms, open concept kitchen & living room - and is situated in a well-maintained subdivision. Adding to its appeal is a fully finished basement, with a portion of the space previously utilized as a theater room and the remaining portion as a mother-in-law suite, offering both privacy and comfort for extended family stays. In addition, the upper-level loft presents an ideal space for setting up a home office, facilitating a perfect work-from-home environment.
